column5: Finally! I decided to rank every film based in Marvel Comics characters, from that weird 1970's Dr. Strange movie and beyond. The movies ranked here will be just the ones from this list here. I will not consider any movie is really a special from an already existing show, like those from "The Incredible Hulk". As always, I will update as I watch them. And yes, I've already watched most of them, but I like to rank it fresh, you know?
